(31, '05 DAYS MEDAN â€“ LAKE TOBA HOLIDAYS', 'Enjoying Lake Toba : one of the awesome natural wonders of the world.<br>Experience and enjoying Lake Toba : a scenic and pretty Volcanic Lake.<br>Explore the Magnificent of huge lake in Sumatra <br>					                                ', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m52!1m12!1m3!1d1019916.441526838!2d98.25738066376086!3d3.081703226437901!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!4m37!3e0!4m5!1s0x30314a34dfa5662d%3A0xc536c90019a09ea6!2sKualanamu%20International%20Airport%2C%20Jalan%20Bandara%20Kuala%20Namu%2C%20Pasar%20Enam%20Kuala%20Namu%2C%20Deli%20Serdang%20Regency%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.6338253999999997!2d98.87730169999999!4m5!1s0x303131cc1c3eb2fd%3A0x23d431c8a6908262!2sMedan%2C%20Medan%20City%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.5951956!2d98.67222269999999!4m5!1s0x3031845c5ac9d49d%3A0xec50414d3469acee!2sPematangsiantar%2C%20Pematang%20Siantar%20City%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d2.965147!2d99.0626377!4m5!1s0x3031e8022c23c201%3A0x9e185a1f1c3da745!2sSamosir%2C%20Samosir%20Regency%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d2.6273112!2d98.7922018!4m5!1s0x3031028adff333f9%3A0x5eba62355c88647b!2sBerastagi%2C%20Gundaling%20II%2C%20Karo%20Regency%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.185291!2d98.504913!4m5!1s0x303131cc1c3eb2fd%3A0x23d431c8a6908262!2sMedan%2C%20Medan%20City%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.5951956!2d98.67222269999999!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1576950941128!5m2!1sen!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>', '                                                    <b>DAY 01: AIRPORT â€“ HOTEL / CITY TOURÂ Â  (Emerald Garden Hotel/ Le Polonia Hotel / similar)<br></b>Arrival at Kualanamu International Airport Medan, meet and transfer to hotel and then city tour by visiting Great Mosque, Sultan Palace, Chinese Temple and market, afterwards return back to hotel.<br><br><b>DAY 02: MEDAN â€“ SAMOSIR (Tabo Cottages / Samosir villa)Â Â Â Â  (B)<br></b>After breakfast drive to Parapat via Tebing Tinggi, on the way stop at several plantation for rubber, and oilpalm , arrival at Parapat crossing to Samosir Island by ferry boat and arriving on Samosir check-in to Hotel.<br><br><b>DAY 03: SAMOSIR â€“ EXCURSIONÂ Â  (B)<br></b>After breakfast excursion by car or boat on Lake Toba and visiting several Batak Toba traditional villages at :<br>- TomokÂ Â Â Â Â  : To see the old tombs of Sidabutar Kings.<br>- AmbaritaÂ  : To see stone chairs and tables, the execution place of Sialagan Kings.<br>- Simanindo: To see Batak traditional dances (Tor-Tor) and Museum. Afternoon return back to hotel.<br><br><b>DAY 04: SAMOSIR â€“ BRASTAGI (Hotel Sinabung Hills / Sibayak Intl Hotel / Grand Mutiara Hotel)Â Â  (B)<br></b>After breakfast crossing back to Parapat and then drive to Brastagi via Simarjarunjung with stop at Rumah Bolon (Long House) the old Palace of Batak Simalungun Kings, Sipiso-piso waterfall and,Â  Batak Karo traditional village at Dokan, arrival at Brastagi visiting fruit market, Gundaling hill. Afternoon check-in to hotel.<br><br><b>DAY 05: BRASTAGI â€“ MEDAN / AIRPORTÂ Â  (B)<br></b>After breakfast drive to Medan by passing Sibolangit and Sembahe, upon arrival at Medan, directly transferred to Airport. Tour Ends<br><br>                                                                                                        '),
(32, '05 DAYS MEDAN â€“ TANGKAHAN â€“ BUKIT LAWANG PLUS RAFTING', 'Explore Tangkahan the hidden paradise of Gunung Leuser National Park<br>Discover Sumatra Orang Utan & Great Rapids Adventure of Wampu River rafting<br>A true wilderness experience, see Sumatra Orang Utan and Enjoy river journey.<br>Excelent experience and fantastic tracking to see Sumatra Orang Utan and Rafting at Wampu river<br>					                                					                                					                                ', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m46!1m12!1m3!1d509661.7415905114!2d98.19299246860326!3d3.648382387712278!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!4m31!3e0!4m5!1s0x30314a34dfa5662d%3A0xc536c90019a09ea6!2sKualanamu%20International%20Airport%2C%20Jalan%20Bandara%20Kuala%20Namu%2C%20Pasar%20Enam%20Kuala%20Namu%2C%20Deli%20Serdang%20Regency%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.6338253999999997!2d98.87730169999999!4m5!1s0x303131cc1c3eb2fd%3A0x23d431c8a6908262!2sMedan%2C%20Medan%20City%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.5951956!2d98.67222269999999!4m5!1s0x3030b4c7e67e2c7d%3A0x209df7765468fec3!2sTangkahan%2C%20Namu%20Sialang%2C%20Langkat%20Regency%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.6962631!2d98.0691646!4m5!1s0x3030c81b5f04b997%3A0xd57e31753995db8f!2sBukit%20Lawang%2C%20Langkat%20Regency%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.5552618!2d98.1447804!4m5!1s0x303131cc1c3eb2fd%3A0x23d431c8a6908262!2sMedan%2C%20Medan%20City%2C%20North%20Sumatra!3m2!1d3.5951956!2d98.67222269999999!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1576951193958!5m2!1sen!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>', '<div align=\"justify\">                                                    <b>DAY 01: AIRPORT / MEDAN â€“TANGKAHAN (Mega Inn)Â Â  (B)Â  </b><br>Upon arrival at Kuala Namu Int airport Medan, pick up by our tour guide and then drive toTangkahan via Binjai and BatangSerangan. Afternoon arrival at Tangkahan check-in at MEGA INN<br><br><b>DAY 02: TANGKAHAN â€“ ELEPHANT WASHING & RIVER SAFARI - BUKIT LAWANG ( Bukit Lawang Cottage / RinduAlam Hotel)Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  (B L)<br></b>After breakfast walking to the elephant station and then joinÂ  with the Mahout during washing the Elephant, help feeding the elephants, after feeding the Elephant enjoying Tubing through the river and stop will be made at fantastic Buluh Waterfall where you may enjoy the waterfall, take your natutal shower and then you can enjoy sun bathing or swimming on the river while enjoying picnic lunch on the beach of the river.Afternoon arrival at the village then return to guest house by walking, after a short rest drive to Bukit Lawang by Jeep passing plantation and jungle raod, on the way stop at Plantation and several interesting places such as school, enjoying the panorama and witness the activities of the local people. Upon arrival at Bukit Lawang check-in to hotel and afternoon free at own leisure to enjoy the nature of Bukit Lawang.<br><br><b>DAY 03: FULLDAY LEUSER NATIONAL PARK TRACKINGÂ  (B,L)<br></b>After breakfast walking to the jungle to start a jungle tracking to explore the nature of Leuser National Park with their flora and fauna, the possibility to see Orang Utan on their own habitat and other kind of animal such as Thomas leaf monkeys, long tail macaque, gibbon, black gibbon and other kind of flora and fauna of tropical rain forest. This full day tracking will finish in the afternoon. <br><br><b>DAY 04: FULLDAY WHITE WATER RAFTING - MEDAN (Emerald Garden/ Le Polonia Hotel) B,L<br></b>After breakfast drive by mini bus to Wampuriver and arrival at starting point, starting your white water rafting adventure. An excellent opportunity to see the bird and wild life, as while as enjoying the two mild rapids during the rafting. Arrival at waterfall at the bank of the river enjoying your shower and lunch will be provided afternoon arrival at the stop point pick up by the driver and then drive back to Medan, afternoon arrival in Medan check in to hotel.enjoying coffee break before driving back to hotel.<br><br><b>DAY 05: HOTEL -Â  AIRPORTÂ Â  (B)<br></b>After breakfast free at own leisure until time transfer to airport.<br></div>                                                                                                                                                            ');
